data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located right off of US-1N is a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Featuring spacious living areas, a fully appointed kitchen with spacious dining room, and a cozy fireplace in the family room, this home offers the ideal setting for both relaxation and entertainment. The property boasts a beautifully landscaped yard, a screened in back porch for relaxing evenings or outdoor gatherings, and a serene neighborhood setting. The Primary Bedroom has an ensuite with a walk-in soaking tub and seperate shower. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home sweet home!
